    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<br><br><br>我的博物馆：寻宝猎人是一款面向教育的第一人称模拟类游戏，转为文物范欣爱好者，探险爱好者，管理经营以及历史爱好者打造。修复你从祖父那里继承的博物馆，重振它的辉煌，赢得游客以及各方人群的好评！<br><br>重振荣耀之路！通过出色的翻新修复玩法，众多的谜题以及历史事件，让这个跨界游戏让你成为博物馆行业的明星。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────</h2><strong>经营你自己的博物馆</strong> - 作为博物馆所有人，在你走向最大的艺术机构的路上你将面临艰难的经营以及财务挑战！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────</h2><strong>维护建筑</strong> - 清洁并且翻新你的博物馆，你需要牢记一个漂亮的地方需要持续地努力。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833710/extras/ab3e7f0a7cd47bf4ed5fea813942450d.poster.avif?t=1748595114\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833710/extras/ab3e7f0a7cd47bf4ed5fea813942450d.webm?t=1748595114\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833710/extras/ab3e7f0a7cd47bf4ed5fea813942450d.mp4?t=1748595114\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────</h2><strong>探索未知的地方</strong> - 在遥远的地方进行探索，揭开谜题，为你的博物馆获得独特的展品。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833710/extras/308b111a0fb70df640adc788570370b5.poster.avif?t=1748595114\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833710/extras/308b111a0fb70df640adc788570370b5.webm?t=1748595114\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833710/extras/308b111a0fb70df640adc788570370b5.mp4?t=1748595114\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833710/extras/8bb1e20abb3d1532fb4afdb6f1d7eb88.poster.avif?t=1748595114\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833710/extras/8bb1e20abb3d1532fb4afdb6f1d7eb88.webm?t=1748595114\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833710/extras/8bb1e20abb3d1532fb4afdb6f1d7eb88.mp4?t=1748595114\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────</h2><strong>修复文物</strong> - 修复你获得的老旧以及损坏的文物，让他们重获新生。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833710/extras/e92f66186c1af40414997b5c949475d1.poster.avif?t=1748595114\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833710/extras/e92f66186c1af40414997b5c949475d1.webm?t=1748595114\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833710/extras/e92f66186c1af40414997b5c949475d1.mp4?t=1748595114\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833710/extras/9e2a7e57221e91d28b5b6509fb9ea345.poster.avif?t=1748595114\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833710/extras/9e2a7e57221e91d28b5b6509fb9ea345.webm?t=1748595114\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833710/extras/9e2a7e57221e91d28b5b6509fb9ea345.mp4?t=1748595114\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────</h2><strong>举办展会</strong>- 展出你所获得的文物，举办一场最棒的展览吧。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833710/extras/da9bd4696b2d68663e3c50e3b3038322.poster.avif?t=1748595114\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833710/extras/da9bd4696b2d68663e3c50e3b3038322.webm?t=1748595114\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833710/extras/da9bd4696b2d68663e3c50e3b3038322.mp4?t=1748595114\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
